      "title": "Standing Cable Glute Kickbacks",
      "notes": "This OR machine.\n\nTarget: 2 Technical Failure (RPE 10).\n\nLengthened partials: Immediately after third set, log as drop set.\n\nOrdering: Perform before Abductions. Prevents standing leg exhaustion.\n\nIsolation: Targeted glute peak. Stable standing leg required.\n\nVector: Kick back and 30° out.\n\nSetup: Stand on 2.5kg plate. Elevate standing foot for ground clearance.\n\nLogging: Weight/Reps for one side only.",
